{"tid":1822861,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"伊朗當局據報以實彈及催淚彈驅散反政府示威者","createTime":"2020-01-13T08:18:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-13T08:43:44.000Z","uid":240362,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"6aac6548b5f908f235171ac0e7b833bd4c992231","tid":1822861,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T08:18:06.000Z","msg":"伊朗首都德黑蘭星期日再有大批民眾上街，抗議當局最初否認擊落烏克蘭客機，警方及安全部隊據報發射實彈及催淚彈驅散。美聯社引述一個駐伊朗的國際人權組織說，收到民眾提供的影片，顯示有催淚彈落在當地一個廣場附近，民眾爭相走避。亦有影片顯示，一名女子的腳懷疑中槍，不停流血，地下留有大灘血漬。組織要求伊朗政府，容許人民依法進行和平抗議活動。美國總統特朗普早前警告伊朗，不要殺害示威者，又說全世界都注視伊朗局勢。<br />\n<br />\n2020-01-13 16:04:42"},{"pid":"d6786ad8e7f7f0fd2065967a9956ab5d56a88394","tid":1822861,"uid":310446,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T08:28:45.000Z","msg":"仗都唔駛打就自爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f30ab7bb9254e296105941fe26b179c93f1af4a","tid":1822861,"uid":91432,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T08:30:00.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: green;\">伊朗</span> = <span style=\"color: red;\">左膠</span>摯愛</strong></span>"},{"pid":"9b0b4e5b5329a59f6710e95a9b6880abdcc95a9c","tid":1822861,"uid":180124,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T08:31:22.000Z","msg":"內憂外患<br />\n哩啲一打根本即刻摺埋"},{"pid":"5d98cc99ea218674c719abe67109975890c10758","tid":1822861,"uid":43041,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T08:32:32.000Z","msg":"伊斯蘭國家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />自相殘殺到滅族就最好"},{"pid":"341e65e75004296e769fe85e5ac269ab6660c22f","tid":1822861,"uid":195998,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T08:35:49.000Z","msg":"左膠:  睇唔到"},{"pid":"c6fd7760f4e5acb2378e13523ccdb4c1529d50e6","tid":1822861,"uid":254383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T08:40:15.000Z","ms